this is not my beautiful house . . . think a christmas carrol with a modern-day twist to it and you 've got family man . a tale of a man who chose buisness over pleasure . when told that he would get a higher-paying job out in the big city , he agreed to fly over there and take it . . . leaving his girlfriend behind who wanted to marry him really badly . he promised that he would come back and everything but never did . now , a few years later , he is the rich and fancy buisness man that he always wanted to be . but , one night he is confronted by a man who claims that he can give him a glmipse of what his future might have been . now it 's come true . and now he 's trying to get his buisness future back